* She avoided the fireball and darts but Prowls claws were another story. 
Already feeling one hitch into her back and rip a nice sized gash in it 
while the impact almost send her stomach to the ground.
Back legs were the most powerful part on the body because they had the mose 
muscle and force begind them , thanking the Maxtrix now that nothing was 
broken.
This happend so fast, though, that she had no real time to realize that 
Prowl had actually got mad and attacked her.
< Must be the beast mode.> She thought while she moved to the side a bit.
Prowl could get himself killed unless he either mastered it in a short time 
or was removed of it.  To remove it would be easy, she would just have to 
transform back, or she hoped that it would work that way. But she wasn't 
going to try it just yet.
She was a bit too pissed off to do that.
Iron Raptor roared and jumped, hoping to get a hand or hip, either would do 
just fine. She just wanted to get Prowl down onto the ground where she could 
deal with him better and his advantage of the air would be gone.*
